Name     &OThe South Road&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A dusty trail follows the coastline south from Ratchet. To the east, the
waves of the Great Sea crash against the rocks. To the west, the arid
plains of the Southern Barrens begin to take hold.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26516
