Name     &OThe Tideskipper Wreck&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The remains of a massive human vessel lie shattered on the rocks here.
Debris is scattered across the sand, and the area has been claimed by
a group of aggressive pirates who use the wreck as a base.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26519
Desc      The South Road.
~
