#ROOM
Vnum     26521
Name     &OThe Gold Road - Southern Barrens&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The savannah here feels even more desolate. The grass is thinner, and
the heat is more oppressive. Massive thunderhawks circle high above,
waiting for something to succumb to the elements.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26512
Desc      Southern Junction.
~
#ENDEXIT
