#ROOM
Vnum     26522
Name     &OCamp Taurajo&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A modest Tauren settlement serves as a waypoint for travelers heading
south. Several large hide tents and a central fire pit provide a place
to rest. The scent of sweetgrass and leather is strong here.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26521
Desc      The Gold Road.
~
