Direction west~
ToRoom    26523
Desc      Field of Giants.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26523
Name     &OThe Field of Giants&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The earth is littered with the colossal bones of ancient creatures.
Massive ribcages and skulls rise from the dust like monuments. It is
a somber place, filled with the echoes of a prehistoric age.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    26522
Desc      Camp Taurajo.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26504 3 26523
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26524
Name     &OPath to the Great Lift&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The terrain drops away suddenly as you approach the southern edge of the
plateau. A massive wooden structure, powered by heavy pulleys and
counterweights, stands ready to lower travelers into the canyon below.
Massive walls of thorny vines rise to the east and west, the strongholds
of the quilboar.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26522
Desc      Camp Taurajo.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    26525
Desc      The Great Lift.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    26532
Desc      A path carved through massive briars leads to Razorfen Kraul.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    26533
Desc      A dark, thorn-choked path leads to Razorfen Downs.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26532
Name     &ORazorfen Kraul - The Bramble Maze&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Giant, razor-sharp thorns form a natural fortress here, the ancestral
home of the Razorfen quilboar tribe. The grunting of the beast-men can
be heard from every direction. At the end of the path, a swirling instance
portal blocks the entrance to their inner sanctum.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    26524
Desc      The path to the Great Lift.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction in~
ToRoom    26930
Desc      Step through the portal into Razorfen Kraul.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26533
Name     &yRazorfen Downs - The Murder Hole&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The massive thorn walls here are dead and rotting, infected by a dark,
necromantic blight. The air is thick with the smell of decay. Undead
quilboar shamble in the distance, and a swirling purple portal marks the
entrance to the Scourge-infected depths.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    26524
Desc      The path to the Great Lift.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26525
Name     &OThe Great Lift&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand on a large wooden platform suspended by thick hempen ropes.
Looking down, you can see the orange, needle-like mesas of Thousand
Needles far below. This is the only safe way down the cliffs.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26524
Desc      The path back.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    28500
Desc      Down to Thousand Needles.
~
#ENDEXIT
