#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26526
Name     &CThe Lush Oasis&d~
Sector   water_swim~
Desc     Located in the southeastern corner of the Barrens, this oasis is a
paradise of greenery and clear water. However, the beauty is deceptive,
as the area is heavily guarded by the warlike centaur tribes. A gaping
cavern entrance shaped like a giant beast's skull leads deep underground.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    26521
Desc      Back to the Gold Road.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    26531
Desc      A dark cavern smelling of damp earth and raptors.
~
