#ROOM
Vnum     26531
Name     &gWailing Caverns - The Pool of Tears&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The air in this underground cavern is incredibly humid and smells
strongly of ozone and overgrown vegetation. Vines hang from the ceiling,
and the sound of weeping echoes through the tunnels. A glowing blue portal
swirls before you, leading into the heart of the Wailing Caverns. 
~
Exit
Direction up~
ToRoom    26526
Desc      Back to the surface.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26527
Name     &OThe Dreadmist Peak&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A jagged, obsidian-colored mountain rises from the northern plains.
Dark, swirling mists cling to its slopes, and the air feels cold and
unnatural. It is a place of dark rituals and shadow magic.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    26528
Desc      Back to the road.
~
